        "Description": "Good morning 47. Today you get to return to Dartmoor Manor again. Today&apos;s first targets have bought the manor named Edward Carlisle and his wife Rebecca Carlisle, and Edwards brother Gregory Carlisle and his wife Emma Carlisle, They look normal, but are actually running some kind of secret weapons operation and terrorism. Phenas Whitmer is too one of the targets. He is an undercover cop who the Carlisles have hired to tell the authorities that nothing illegal is going on at the manor. Have fun!",
